  "detailed_description": "Moontrain is a dynamic point & click adventure game. The story follows a detective who needs to solve an impossible case. Everyone who tried to solve it had no luck, maybe you are just the detective we need. <br />\r\nEnter a surreal and mysterious world. Try to find clues and solve puzzles. Play challenging mini games that are not just for fun, this is serious detective work.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe Moontrain is departing from the station, all aboard!",
